data.description: Welcome to this beautifully laid out home that includes many perks including three bedrooms all included on the upper floor. A full bathroom upstairs and a half bathroom on the main level with the main level including a HUGE living room and a huge family room with a wood burning fireplace connected to a formal dining room and a walkthrough kitchen. The home is perfectly located near downtown and is walking distance to the fairgrounds come summer time. The garage is an OVER sized two stall garage with the yard including a partially fenced in area. Great neighbors with a high quality air conditioning unit and furnace installed in 2014, this home has it all. Take a look today!
